                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I am Lady Moira Glenshannon, and I welcome you all to our first class on First Aid. As Heroes, we all must face danger. The purpose of this class is to help you survive injuries as well as to be able to help others.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "cf0e9a31-18d3-4f0f-b432-e6cb9996b7ea",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "In this class, you will learn the basics of treating injuries. You will learn to identify and use natural remedies. You will also learn how to make pills and potions that promote healing.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "aec783f4-364d-4176-ba5d-22e351c25a76",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "While there will be some lectures, there will also be time spent working with plants and fungi in the garden. After all, fresh air and sunshine help heal the spirit.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "cbc1c8bd-bd30-42fb-9add-5c01ce7b38cd",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions you would like to ask before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
