                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "You say we will learn how to make healing pills and potions... Is this something we can do, say, at home?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b65ff494-edab-4b2b-81b5-2dd2d241f24f",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Healing potions and pills are a little more complex than putting a few ingredients together to make a cake. You do need specialized equipment and extremely rare ingredients.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5d9cb9c6-76ec-465e-9b32-fe1b0bfd35a0",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, we will have sessions devoted to making remedies here, and you will be able to take the remedies away with you. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
