                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "We're supposed to work in the garden and make potions and stuff... So the infirmary gets restocked and other people can be healed?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2023ff6d-6b42-47a9-8f6f-618bf9e77375",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes... and so when you are injured at any time, you can come to the infirmary and be healed. This is a school for Heroes, and we tend to get hurt. We also do what we can to heal others. That's what heroes do.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
